==友好城市==
格拉纳达的[[友好城市|友好城市]]有：<ref name=TwinCity>{{cite web|url=http://www.granada.org/v2010.nsf/xxtod/ciudadeshermanas |title=CIUDADES CON LAS QUE ESTÁ HERMANADA GRANADA |type=official website |publisher=Ayuntamiento de Granada |location=Granada, Spain |language=es |accessdate=2014-12-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141115060126/http://granada.org/v2010.nsf/xxtod/ciudadeshermanas |archivedate=2014-11-15}}</ref>

* {{flag|FRA}} [[普罗旺斯地区艾克斯|普罗旺斯地区艾克斯]]（1979）<ref name=TwinCity/>
* {{flag|MAR}} [[得土安|得土安]]（1988）<ref name=TwinCity/>
* {{flag|ALG}} [[特莱姆森|特莱姆森]]（1989）<ref name=TwinCity/>
* {{flag|USA}} [[科勒尔盖布尔斯|科勒尔盖布尔斯]]（1989）<ref name=TwinCity/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.coralgables.com/index.aspx?page=330 |title=City of Coral Gables : Sister Cities |publisher=City of Coral Gables |date=2014 |accessdate=2014-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150613234035/http://www.coralgables.com/index.aspx?page=330 |archive-date=2015-06-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
* {{flag|GER}} [[弗莱堡|弗莱堡]]（1991）<ref name=TwinCity/>
* {{flag|MAR}} [[马拉喀什|马拉喀什]]（1994）<ref name=TwinCity/>
* {{flag|BRA}} [[贝洛奥里藏特|贝洛奥里藏特]]（2002）<ref name=TwinCity/>
* {{flag|UAE}} [[沙迦_(城市)|沙迦]]（2009）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.uaeinteract.com/docs/Sultan_attends_signing_of_Sharjah-Granada_sister_city_agreement/34150.htm |title=Sultan attends signing of Sharjah-Granada sister city agreement UAE – The Official Web Site – News |publisher=Uaeinteract.com |date= |accessdate=2010-10-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/69goM3dVj?url=http://www.uaeinteract.com/docs/Sultan_attends_signing_of_Sharjah-Granada_sister_city_agreement/34150.htm |archivedate=2012-08-05}}</ref>

